      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable and stylish ride? This car is in great shape and ready for its next adventure! It has been well-maintained and drives beautifully, showing only the typical, minor wear you'd expect from a car that's been enjoyed responsibly. It's a fantastic, solid choice for anyone seeking quality and performance at a great value!",
