    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold as-is, ideal for a mechanic's project or a parts donor. The exterior shows significant wear, including rust spots and faded paint, while the interior requires a deep clean and repair of several torn upholstery sections. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and will need immediate professional attention to be roadworthy again. While it offers a solid foundation for restoration, please expect to invest time and resources into bringing it back to life.",
