    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is, making it an ideal candidate for a mechanical project or a parts car. The engine currently struggles to start and requires significant repair, and the transmission shows signs of imminent failure. Externally, the body has multiple deep dents, significant rust along the rocker panels, and heavily oxidized paint. The interior reflects years of heavy use with several large tears in the upholstery, a cracked dashboard, and non-functional electronics.",
